I don't know if anyone else has found it, but Silver Suezo (suezo/???) for the PAL version can be aquired from westlife (all it says on the front of the case is Westlife and its on a blue/gray backdrop).

Stats:

Lif: 90
Pow: 139
Int: 151
Ski: 107
Spd: 105
Def: 134

Likes: Rest
Dislikes: Battle
Nature: Bad

Stupid monster ;)

Techs:

Starts with: Tail attack, spit, kiss.

Hope this helps you PAL gamers out there.
